HEADWORD: Continuator
<hw>Con*tin"u*a`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>continuateur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who, or that which, continues;
esp., one who continues a series or a work; a continuer.</def>
<rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
